==Romanian==
===Etymology===
A pre-Roman substratum word. Probably via [[W:Dacian language|Dacian]] from [[PIE]] *bhereg-, "white". The Romanian word is akin to Albanian ''[[bardhë]]''. This bird is called "white" also in the Slavic languages, compare Croatian ''[[labud]]''.
===Noun===
'''barză''' ''f'' (pl. ''berze'')

